RottenEggs App/API Example - Badges
=====================

What is this?
----------------------
This is an example of how an app can be developed using the RottenEggs API 
framework.  It is written in PHP and requires MySQL, a standard LAMP setup is
recommended.

Download
--------
You can download the current version of the app via git/github.
git://github.com/rotteneggs/RottenEggs-App-Example---Badges.git

Requirements
------------
* php 5.1+  (with JSON, CURL extensions)
* mysql (see database schema)
* web server (apache,lighttpd,nginx)
* curl with extension for php (yum install php-curl)
* API key from RottenEggs.com
